'''Diagonal''' ke mola o o tlhamaletseng o o kgabaganyang go tshwaraganya dihuku.  Mola o o kgabaganyang ga o ye thwi kwa godimo, kwa tlase, kgotsa go kopana. Ke mola o o tshwaraganyang dihuku tse pedi tsa popego.   

Mo dipalong [[mathematics]], "mola-kgabaganyo" o na le bokao jo bo farologaneng. Sekao, mo geometry  diagonal ke mola mongwe le mongwe o o yang magareng a dihuku tsa  polygon.  Ka jalo khutlo-nne, square , e na le didiagonal tse pedi, mme popego e e matlhakore-tlhano, five-sided shape, e na le didiagonal tse tlhano. Ka kakaretso palo ya diagonal e ka supiwa ka  formula [n(n-3)]/2 moo n e leng is the palo yotlhe ya matlhakore a popego.
